"title": "8735: evil, origins of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8735: evil, origins of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Although Scripture does not reveal the ultimate origin of evil, it identifies a number of intermediate sources.</p>\n<h2>Satan as a source of evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1\">GEN 3:1</a></strong> <em>Identified later (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">Rev 12:9</a>) with Satan</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1\">MAT 4:1</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:13\">MRK 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:2\">LUK 4:2</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:1\">1CH 21:1</a> <em>Satan incites David to take a census of Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:11\">JOB 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:5\">JOB 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:37\">MAT 5:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:38-Matt13:39\">MAT 13:38–13:39</a> <em>the parable of the weeds</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a> <em>Satan is responsible for a woman's crippling disease</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:2\">JHN 13:2</a> <em>The devil prompts Judas to betray Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:15\">JHN 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a> <em>Ananias lies to the Holy Spirit at Satan's instigation</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a> <em>Paul's thorn in the flesh from Satan</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">EPH 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:18\">1TH 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:12\">1JN 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1JN 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:2\">REV 20:2</a></p>\n<h2>Other evil powers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:39\">LUK 9:39</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17-Mark9:18\">MRK 9:17–9:18</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:23\">JDG 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:14\">1SA 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10-1Sam18:11\">1SA 18:10–18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:9-1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:9–19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:45\">MAT 12:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:26\">LUK 11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:7\">REV 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:13-Rev16:14\">REV 16:13–16:14</a></p>\n<h2>Fallen human nature as a source of evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:13-Jas1:14\">JAS 1:13–1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:21\">GEN 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:18\">PRO 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:11\">ECC 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:3\">ECC 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:7\">ISA 59:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:14\">JER 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:12\">JER 18:12</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:25\">23:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:39\">LUK 11:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:27-Matt23:28\">MAT 23:27–23:28</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:14-Rom7:23\">ROM 7:14–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:10</a> <em>the love of money a root of evil</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:6\">JAS 3:6</a> <em>The tongue is a source of evil</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:1\">JAS 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>Physical evil is a consequence of moral evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17\">GEN 3:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:20-Deut28:24\">DEU 28:20–28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:58-Deut28:59\">DEU 28:58–28:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:8-Ps90:9\">PSA 90:8–90:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:30\">PRO 14:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:6\">MAL 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19-Rom8:21\">ROM 8:19–8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:1\">REV 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5-Rev16:6\">REV 16:5–16:6</a></p>",
